narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you like Graphic Design, take it. Be prepared to put in a lot of hours for a final product. If you are lukewarm about Graphic Design, don't take it. The kids who are passionate excel and the kids who aren't just end up falling by the wayside. If you don't have a lot of CS4 experience, you are going to get wupped for the first half of semester; self-discipline and a resilient attitude will get you through to the end. Cream will rise...

This class taught me a lot about my creative process, and forced me to look at my designs with both formal and conceptual rigor. The workload is not bad at all and Pamela makes class fun. I'd recommend it.
